title: Tate Modern
name: Tate Modern
description:
This is a really popular spot at The Tate Modern (London) for photographers. The brutalist concrete architecture and sweeping lines make it a dream to shoot, and this is my take on that scene.
The angle at which the image is made and the processing in black and white, really helps to accentuate the curves and lines and the presence of the lone person gives the sense of scale.
